Gretchen Mol https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gretchen_Mol 0 Gretchen Mol (born November 8, 1972) is an American actress and former model. She is known for her roles in the films Rounders, Celebrity, 3:10 to Yuma, The Thirteenth Floor, and The Notorious Bettie Page, in which she played the title character. She also appeared as Gillian Darmody in HBO's Boardwalk Empire. Gretchen_Mol ( born November_8_,_1972 ) is an_American_actress and former_model .
